Spec: Shared Plugin Files

Purpose:
  Own files copied into every generated product plugin output.

Owns:
  ./CONTRIBUTING.md
  ./SECURITY.md
  ./assets/**

Must:
  Store reusable assets and other shared package files used by multiple plugin targets.
  Keep shared files product-neutral.
  Point contributors and security reporters back to `https://github.com/specdd/agent-plugins` for source changes.

Must not:
  Store product-specific manifests or marketplace metadata.
